episodes.title: This Is How a Doomsday Cult Has Been Taking Over Fiji Bit by Bit
episodes.description: In 2014, South Korean believers arrived in Fiji with a terrifying prophecy: nuclear apocalypse was coming, and this Pacific island was humanity's only refuge. What happened next is one of the most disturbing infiltrations of a national economy you've never heard about. Let’s explore how a doomsday cult has been taking over Fiji slowly, quietly, and strategically—not through violence, but through businesses, farms, faith, and control.
